org.cef.handler

Interface CefRequestContextHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CefRequestContextHandlerAdapter 

    public interface CefRequestContextHandler
    Implement this interface to provide handler implementations.(实现此接口以提供处理程序实现。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      CefResourceRequestHandler getResourceRequestHandler(CefBrowser browser, CefFrame frame, CefRequest request, boolean isNavigation, boolean isDownload, java.lang.String requestInitiator, BoolRef disableDefaultHandling)
      Called on the IO thread before a resource request is initiated.(在启动资源请求之前在IO线程上调用。)

    • Method Detail

      • getResourceRequestHandler

        CefResourceRequestHandler getResourceRequestHandler(CefBrowser browser,
                                                    CefFrame frame,
                                                    CefRequest request,
                                                    boolean isNavigation,
                                                    boolean isDownload,
                                                    java.lang.String requestInitiator,
                                                    BoolRef disableDefaultHandling)
        Called on the IO thread before a resource request is initiated. The |browser| and |frame| values represent the source of the request. This method will not be called if the client associated with |browser| returns a non-null value from CefRequestHandler.getResourceRequestHandler for the same request (identified by CefRequest.getIdentifier).(在启动资源请求之前在IO线程上调用。|browser|和|frame|值表示请求的来源。如果与|browser|关联的客户端对同一请求（由CefRequest.getIdentifier标识）从CefRequestHandler.getResourceRequestHandler返回非空值，则不会调用此方法。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        request - The request itself. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(request-请求本身。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        isNavigation - True if the resource request is a navigation.(isNavigation-如果资源请求是导航，则为True。)
        isDownload - True if the resource request is a download.(isDownload-如果资源请求是下载，则为True。)
        requestInitiator - The origin (scheme + domain) of the page that initiated the request.(requestInitiator-发起请求的页面的来源（scheme + domain）。)
        disableDefaultHandling - Set to true to disable default handling of the request, in which case it will need to be handled via CefResourceRequestHandler.getResourceHandler or it will be canceled.(disableDefaultHandling-设置为true可禁用请求的默认处理，在这种情况下，需要通过CefResourceRequestHandler.getResourceHandler进行处理，否则将被取消。)
        Returns:
        A CefResourceRequestHandler instance or null.(CefResourceRequestHandler实例或null。)
